author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-CyberOptics Reports Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.07
text:
Feb 20 (Reuters) - CyberOptics Corp:
* CYBEROPTICS REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER OPERATING RESULTS * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.07 * ‍ Q4 SALES, TOTALED $13.2 MILLION, COMPARED TO $13.5 MILLION IN Q4 OF 2016​
* ‍ ENDED Q4 OF 2017 WITH AN ORDER BACKLOG OF $11.4 MILLION, UP MODESTLY FROM LEVEL AT END OF Q3​
* ‍SALES OF $12.5 - $13.5 MILLION ARE CURRENTLY FORECASTED FOR Q1 OF 2018 ENDING MARCH 31​
* ‍ SALES OF $12.5 MILLION - $13.5 MILLION ARE CURRENTLY FORECASTED FOR Q1 OF 2018​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
